An series of severe thunderstorms has formed from Inwood west across Lake Manitoba. Thunderstorms are moving east at 50 km/h. ### Remember, severe thunderstorms can produce tornadoes. Severe thunderstorm warnings are issued when imminent or occurring thunderstorms are likely to produce or are producing one or more of the following: large hail, damaging winds, torrential rainfall.
